Many of you will know Phil Oakley from the quality of the research, investment articles and investing presentations he has delivered and completed over the years. For those few of you that are not familiar with Phil you can find that comprehensive interview with him here https://www.conkers3.com/phil-oakley/  that he gave on #CONKERSCORNER of his own insightful journey in the Investment industry and beyond. His insights and knowledge are sought after by institutions and private investors alike. Phil is currently the Associate Editor of the Investors Chronicle magazine. 

The outstanding quality of Phil's research and educational articles for the Investors' Chronicle were recognised by his peers in June of this year. When Phil won the 2020 CFA Journalist of the Year award. 

At the time of this interview with Phil in late 2020, Investors, Fund Managers, Traders, savers and all participant in the investment markets had already endured a highly volatile and psychologically testing ten months in the markets. 


